_sText:
So Basically This Is my First map, Be Kind ;)

The map is very much in almost perfect symmetry. both teams will have to shoot out the glass in-front of them
swim up shoot out then next bit of glass and the Fight will begin.


Terrorist's:

Get up to the 2nd floor and fend back any Counter terrorist Movement and try and work your way up the ladder behind you, get onto the 3rd floor plant and fight off and remaining Counter Terrorists, Finally blow up the 3rd floor of the building.


Counter Terrorist's:

Get up to the 2nd floor and try to eliminate any  terrorist Movement. If any terrorists Make it up the ladder Follow them up yours and try and stop them before a plant Is made.


GOOD LUCK!



P.s 
To The Few Who Have Asked Yes There ARE Hidden Teliporter's, If you Find them They Will Give You An amazing Advantage :)
